OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784812718
OL,3,CCould commuters soon be flying across
OL,4,Cthe capital in air taxis?
OL,6,FVirgin Atlantic has signed a deal
OL,7,Fwhich could see electric flying taxis
OL,8,Fin London before the end of the decade.
OL,10,FThe airline has joined forces with an
OL,11,FAmerican company, Joby Aviation, which
OL,12,Fis developing a battery powered plane
OL,13,Fwhich can take off vertically.
OL,15,FThe air taxi seats four people and
OL,16,Fwould travel from central London to
OL,17,FHeathrow Airport in less than 10
OL,18,Fminutes.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
