OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784812718
OL,3,CCould commuters soon be flying across
OL,4,Cthe capital in air taxis?
OL,6,FThis morning, Business Secretary
OL,7,FJonathon Reynolds announced a six
OL,8,Fhundred million pound package to back
OL,9,FBritish aerospace.
OL,11,FThe majority of this will go towards
OL,12,Faerospace research and technology
OL,13,Fprojects, like air taxis, for greener
OL,14,Fair travel.
OL,16,FBonny Simi, President of Operations at
OL,17,FJoby Air Taxi's said:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784812718
OL,3,CCould commuters soon be flying across
OL,4,Cthe capital in air taxis?
OL,6,F"The idea is you'll open up your phone
OL,7,Fand you can pick, if you want to buy a
OL,8,Fcar taxi or you want to buy an air
OL,9,Ftaxi.
OL,11,F"The air taxi comes and you go to the
OL,12,Fvertiport, which is like a heliport,
OL,13,Fand you take off vertically.
OL,15,F"Then these propulsion units, not
OL,16,Fengines because they're not engines,
OL,17,Fthey'll move forward and it flies like
OL,18,Fa plane.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784812718
OL,3,CCould commuters soon be flying across
OL,4,Cthe capital in air taxis?
OL,6,F"So it takes off like a helicopter,
OL,7,Fflies like a plane, and lands back as
OL,8,Fa helicopter, and it's very quiet,
OL,9,Flike an electric car is quiet, and
OL,10,Fit's all sustainable."
OL,12,FThe aircrafts are known as eVTOLs,
OL,13,Fwhich stands for electic vertical take-
OL,14,Foff and landing.
OL,16,FThey are designed to operate
OL,17,Fautonomously, although currently still
OL,18,Frequire human oversight.
OL,20,FHeathrow and Gatwick airport have both
OL,21,Fbeen suggested as good landing points.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
