OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784812718
OL,3,CCould commuters soon be flying across
OL,4,Cthe capital in air taxis?
OL,6,FSimi continued:J"In central London,
OL,7,Fperhaps we can land along the River
OL,8,FThames and multi-car parking garages.
OL,10,F"Nobody likes to park on the top level
OL,11,Fof a parking garage- well we do.
OL,13,F"There's several different malls and
OL,14,Fparking garages we're looking at."
OL,16,FAir taxis hope to dramatically
OL,17,Fdecrease journey times. Simi said:
OL,19,F"A very classic case is if you live
OL,20,Fperhaps in the Canary Wharf area or
OL,21,Fsomewhere along the Thames.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784812718
OL,3,CCould commuters soon be flying across
OL,4,Cthe capital in air taxis?
OL,6,F"And if you want to get to Heathrow,
OL,7,Fit might take #100 in a taxi and take
OL,8,F1 hour and 35 minutes.
OL,10,F"It might take a similar amount of
OL,11,Ftime or maybe longer if you're going
OL,12,Fto take, you know, the tube and you
OL,13,Fknow connecting in to take the express.
OL,15,F"That whole thing takes an hour, 1
OL,16,Fhour and 45 minutes and this- it'll
OL,17,Ftake about 8 minutes.
OL,19,F"So that's the type of seamless
OL,20,Fjourney people can be looking forward
OL,21,Fto."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
