OL,3,CCould commuters soon be flying across
OL,4,Cthe capital in air taxis?
OL,6,FThe rival, British version of the
OL,7,Faircraft is called Valo. It's being
OL,8,Fdeveloped by the firm Vertical
OL,9,FAerospace.
OL,11,FYesterday, the company announced it is
OL,12,Fin advanced discussions with the
OL,13,FGovernment on a support package for
OL,14,Fmillions of additional funding.
OL,16,FIt says this is "a major vote of
OL,17,Fconfidence" in Vertical Aerospace.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/8
