OL,3,CCould commuters soon be flying across
OL,4,Cthe capital in air taxis?
OL,6,FVertical Aerospace claims its journeys
OL,7,Fwill cost around the same as an Uber,
OL,8,Falthough there has been speculation
OL,9,Fabout this online.
